Class MenuItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • cafe.MenuItem
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Coffee, Donut

    public class MenuItem
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the superclass of all menu items, such as donuts and coffee Any class defined for a menu item must extend this class. All the subclasses must include a “itemPrice” method for calculating the price of the menu item.
    Author:
    Prachiti Atigre, Ujani Patel
